<br />- much more of network than software development ! but it is ok coz most careers are in Network administration. 
<br />- in a resume there was: Modem Software!!, this is called Browser...!
<br />- adding Norton AntiVirus in an IT resume is something stupid!
<br />- PHP and C-Sharp: top programming lanuges not mentioned in the book!</span>
                  
